KeyFrames - Class in org.jdesktop.animation.timing
KeyFrames holds information about the times at which values are sampled (KeyTimes) and the values at those times (KeyValues).
KeyFrames(KeyValues) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyFrames
Simplest variation; determine keyTimes based on even division of 0-1 range based on number of keyValues.
KeyFrames(KeyValues, KeyFrames.InterpolationType) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyFrames
Simple division of time into equal divisions according to the number of values in keyValues, but this constructor also takes an InterpolationType parameter to tell KeyFrames how to interpolate between each value.
KeyFrames(KeyValues, KeyTimes, KeyFrames.InterpolationType) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyFrames
This variant takes both keyValues (values at each point in time) and keyTimes (times at which values are sampled), in addition to InterpolationType.
KeyFrames(KeyValues, KeySplines, KeyTimes, KeyFrames.InterpolationType) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyFrames
Full constructor: caller provides an instance of all key* structures which will be used to calculate between all times in the keyTimes list.
KeyFrames(KeyValues, KeySplines) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyFrames
Utility constructor that assumes even division of times according to size of keyValues and NONLINEAR interpolation if keySplines is not null.
KeyFrames.InterpolationType - Enum in org.jdesktop.animation.timing
Type of interpolation used between each value in KeyValues.
KeySplines - Class in org.jdesktop.animation.timing
KeySplines is used to hold the information about the splines used in a KeyFrames object.
KeySplines(Spline...) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeySplines
This constructor takes a series of Spline to define a set splines.
KeyTimes - Class in org.jdesktop.animation.timing
Stores a list of times from 0 to 1 that are used in calculating interpolated values for ObjectModifier given a matching set of KeyValues and possibly KeySplines for those times.
KeyTimes(float...) - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyTimes
Creates a new instance of KeyTimes.
KeyValues<T> - Class in org.jdesktop.animation.timing
Stores a list of values that correspond to the times in a KeyTimes object.
KeyValues() - Constructor for class org.jdesktop.animation.timing.KeyValues
Callers should create KeyValues structures from the factory methods which create KeyValues subclasses based on the types of values.
